Bob -

My Bad.......

75-79 w/Auto Trans - 2870mm (211 723 555 Q)
  Note: Cable runs to lever on transmission connected by a ball link on
cable end as Bob noted

However, no cable goes from trans to throttle lever on FI.  It is actuated
by a length of rod.  This is necessary for the gear kickdown for
acceleration/passing (if it were only powerful enough ;-)  ).
