> > lengths for the Type 4 Engine on a Bus:
> >
> > 1972 Only Dual Carb - 3678mm (144.82") (211 721 555 J)
> > 73-74 Dual Carb - 3655mm (143.91") (211 721 555 T)
> > 75-79 EFI - 3458mm (136.16") (211 721 555 AA)
> MANUAL tranny only
> auto tranny uses a much shorter cable with a special ball/socket fittin on
> the end.  can't find my notes at the moment' probably in the garage but it
> is in th 3200mm range.
